Name: JJ Smith Shoe
Description:
“Did you hear about this one, folks?

A favorite among fans of the Solis Report late-night comedy football podcast, JJ Smith Shoe Store looks to be wearing the black and yellow for at least one more season. When he’s not burying linebackers and defensive backs with vicious stiff-arms and blocks, he’s usually dancing on rival teams’ logos (and sometimes paying the price for it).

EVO Gridiron Goofs with the “EVO” badge feature slight (or significant) differences across each rarity. Collect them all for the full sequence!

This Rare variant is limited to twenty-five (25). They will not be re-minted.

Name: Lavisker Sean Alt
Description:
“Your favorite influencer’s favorite wide receiver.”

A wide receiver in a running back’s body, Lavisker Sean Alt is a dynamo with the ball in his hands. After an impressive rookie season, fans look ahead to see what he might accomplish with projected first overall pick, quarterback Trigger Larry. Alt’s long locks and sticky fingers are sure to keep touts shouting for seasons to come.

This Platinum variant is limited to ten (10). They will not be re-minted.

Name: Kyle Poots
Description:
“Galvatron? Does anyone even get that reference?”

Regardless of which giant evil robot comes to mind, Kyle Poots is a villain. A menace. What are defenders supposed to do? He’s a jet-propelled Abrams tank with giant soft hands that can just as easily crush a bowling ball or perform open-heart surgery. What a preposterous player. Absurd.

This Platinum variant is limited to ten (10). They will not be re-minted.

Chimney swept, Jesus wept! I kid, I kid, nobody gets buckets like chimney when he starts smoking! Gotta remain bullish on this itinerant all star!

This Based Common CryptoDunk is intended as an accessible entryway into the CryptoDunks collection and is minted in a Limited Edition of 50. Nobody brings the ruckus, like CHIMNEY BUCKETS!

This tall drink of water may be gone, but will never fade away! It's only a shame he's not around to play wingman to Anthony Edwards--now that would take my breath away! The DRINK NOWHISKEY Based Common is intended as a relatively accessible collectors item, but this special Limited Edition of 99 will never be minted again.
